  "text": "Remark 3.2. If we instead use (2.14) for ℓ = 0 we can obtain a proof of the following residue condition for membership in an ideal of germs of smooth functions in Ea, where a ⊂ O. This result was proved in [CITATION_1] in case a is a complete intersection, and for a general ideal, in fact for any submodule a ⊂ O ⊕m , in [CITATION_2] .",
